<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=2998&amp;p=22184#p22184"><![CDATA[
I am looking for a good video capture "tuner" that takes S-video and RCA audio or RCA composite video and audio to USB.  Basically, I want to be able to hook up my SNES to my laptop and play games on it.  So I am not really interested in recording video or watching TV.<br />Any suggestions?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=94">Jagasian</a> — Tue Feb 27, 2007 3:48 pm</p><hr />
